version_description:
Dear friends!
The 100% achievement and small bugs have been improved - we do care about your comfort.
The big arrow helps to let you know that the visitors are on a paving slab.
Also we have fixed the deadlock after the pause.
If you have some remarks, feel free to contact us!
Together we can make the game better!
